%
(Fusion probing subroutine smoke test)
(This only exercises no-motion helper macros so it is safe to run as a parser/interpreter check.)

G90 G94 G17 G40 G49 G80

o<f360_tip_radius> call
#<probe_radius> = #<_value>

o<f360_fast_probe_speed> call
#<fast_probe_speed> = #<_value>

o<f360_slow_probe_speed> call
#<slow_probe_speed> = #<_value>

o<f360_slow_probe_distance> call
#<slow_probe_distance> = #<_value>

o<f360_check_position> call [1.0] [1.0] [0.001] [0]
o<f360_check_size> call [1.0] [1.0] [0.001] [0]
o<f360_check_angle> call [0.0] [0.0] [0.1] [0]

(DEBUG, Fusion smoke test resolved macros successfully.)
(DEBUG, tip_radius=#<probe_radius> fast=#<fast_probe_speed> slow=#<slow_probe_speed> slow_dist=#<slow_probe_distance>)
M2
%
